%description
A MIDI file player/game that displays the musical notes AND teaches you how
to play the piano.

QPiano is a fun way of playing along with a musical accompaniment and
at the same time learning the basics of reading musical notation.
The difference between playing along to a CD or a standard MIDI file
is that QPiano listens and reacts to what you are playing on a
MIDI keyboard.

To run QPiano you need a MIDI Piano Keyboard and a MIDI interface
for the PC. If you don't have a MIDI keyboard you can still try out
QPiano, using the PC keyboard ('x' is middle C), but a MIDI piano
is really recommended.

